'''帕卡'''（'''PACCAR Inc.''' ）是美国[[财富500强|财富500强]]公司<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune500/2012/snapshots/318.html|title=CNN Fortune 500 list|accessdate=June 2013|archive-date=2013-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206040056/http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune500/2012/snapshots/318.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和世界最大的中型和重型[[卡车|卡车]]制造商之一，也有制造轻型和中型车辆。 PACCAR在2006年被授予{{tsl|en|National Medal of Technology|美國国家技术勋章}}(National Medal of Technology)。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ccjdigital.com/paccar-awarded-national-medal-of-technology/|title=Paccar awarded national medal of technology|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2006-02-15|publisher=CCJ digital|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216212545/https://www.ccjdigital.com/paccar-awarded-national-medal-of-technology/|archivedate=2013-12-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.automotiveworld.com/analysis/us-paccar-honoured-with-national-medal-of-technology/|title=PACCAR Inc honored with National Medal of Technology|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2006-02-22|publisher=Automotive World|archive-date=2017-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630154128/https://www.automotiveworld.com/analysis/us-paccar-honoured-with-national-medal-of-technology/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[伦顿_(华盛顿州)|兰顿]]，PACCAR是仍在運營的最古老的企业。 2013年6月该厂还庆祝了它的20周年纪念日；自1993年工廠开始运作已生产了超过13輛萬重型和中型{{tsl|en|Kenworth}}卡车。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.thenewstribune.com/business/2010/11/30/paccar-bringing-back-laid-off-workers-at-renton-kenworth-truck-plant/|title=Paccar Inc bringing back laid off workers|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2010-11-30|publisher={{tsl|en|The News Tribune||The News Tribune}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216224719/http://blog.thenewstribune.com/business/2010/11/30/paccar-bringing-back-laid-off-workers-at-renton-kenworth-truck-plant/|archive-date=2013-12-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ccjdigital.com/kenworth-renton-plant-receives-commuters-honor/|title=Kenworth's Renton plant receives Commuter's award|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2013-06-19|publisher=CCJ Digital Magazine|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200410/https://www.ccjdigital.com/kenworth-renton-plant-receives-commuters-honor/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rentonreporter.com/business/211629591.html|title=Kenworth's Renton Plant Celebrates 20 Years|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2013-06-14|publisher=Renton Reporter|archive-date=2016-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317174011/http://www.rentonreporter.com/business/211629591.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
[[File:Seattle_Car_and_Foundry_Renton_Works_1916.jpg|左]]的工作情況（1916年）]]
PACCAR原名Seattle Car Manufacturing Company，在1905年，由William Pigott, Sr. 以资本10 000美元成立。其原始业务是生产[[鐵路車輛|铁路]]和[[伐木|记录]]设备。1909年，因爲其{{tsl|en|Duwamish River|Duwamish}}工廠為趕及應付大量的订单而毁于火灾，该公司在兰顿建立了一个新的工厂。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.seattle.gov/fleetsfacilities/firelevy/facilities/fs14/pdfs/bolasf14nompart1.pdf|title=King county fire district|accessdate=2013-06-20|publisher=Seattle.gov|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727185559/https://www.seattle.gov/fleetsfacilities/firelevy/facilities/fs14/pdfs/BOLASF14NomPart1.pdf|archivedate=2012-07-27}}</ref>1917年，公司與[[俄勒冈州|俄勒岡州]][[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]]的Twohy Brothers合并；Twohy Brothers是它當時在西岸唯一的竞争对手；同時，公司更名为Pacific Car and Foundry Company。接下来的几年该公司专门设计刹车，無頂的车辆、冷藏货车车厢，用于运输易腐物品和供卡车使用的拖车。<ref name="Pacific Car and Foundry">{{Cite web|url=http://www.midcontinent.org/rollingstock/builders/pacific_car.htm|title=Pacific Car & Foundry/|accessdate=2013-06-20|date=2006-12-30|publisher=midcontinent.org|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227095230/https://www.midcontinent.org/rollingstock/builders/pacific_car.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>该公司还制造手工製钢架，用于建築，並套用在多个西雅图建筑。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20000924&slug=4044996|title=Paccar's rough road|date=2004-09-24|publisher=The Seattle Times|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104195351/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20000924&slug=4044996|dead-url=no}}</ref>在1924年，创始人Willian Pigott把公司控制權售給{{tsl|en|American Car and Foundry Company|American Car and Fondry公司}}。 在1934年，他的儿子Paul Pigott重新获得了公司大部分的控制。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.wsulibs.wsu.edu/cdm/singleitem/collection/clipping/id/27707/rec/2|title=NW History, Lumber Industry & By-products|accessdate=2013-06-25|publisher=[[華盛頓州立大學|WSU Library]]|archive-date=2013-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216205704/http://content.wsulibs.wsu.edu/cdm/singleitem/collection/clipping/id/27707/rec/2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.paccar.com/heritage/default.asp|title=PACCAR Heritage|accessdate=2013-06-26|publisher=Paccar Inc|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509030506/http://www.paccar.com/heritage/default.asp|archivedate=2013-05-09}}</ref>

在1930年代[[大萧条|大萧条]]時，尽管股票市场崩溃，该公司的收益上升，但大萧条加深、令Pacific Car在西北部業務受挫。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.coachbuilt.com/bui/p/pacific_car/pacific_car.htm|title=Pacific Car & Foundry Co.|accessdate=2013-06-18|publisher=Coach bult|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200453/http://www.coachbuilt.com/bui/p/pacific_car/pacific_car.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來公司取得政府合同，提供钢铁用于建造{{tsl|en|Lacey V. Murrow Memorial Bridge|Lacey V. Murrow紀念大橋}}，也从其他公司接收订单。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.lib.washington.edu/imls/kcsnapshots/sets/timeline-text.html|title=King county timeline|accessdate=2013-06-26|publisher=[[華盛頓州立大學|WSU Library]]|archive-date=2012-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121214002334/http://content.lib.washington.edu/imls/kcsnapshots/sets/timeline-text.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 第二次世界大战期间 ===
在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间，Pacific Car的销售額增加，由於用于飞机、机场、桥梁、军舰、高速公路和其他设备的钢材需求增加。公司提供建设美国的基础设施的物資来支持战争。公司也为波音公司承包建造[[B-17轟炸機|B-17轰炸机]]機翼。在1942年春天，公司还为[[美国陆军|美国陆军]]製造[[M4雪曼戰車|M4A1]]坦克。公司可以自己铸造几乎所有坦克的零件。其他车辆包括[[M25戰車運輸車|M25运输车]]和[[T28超重型坦克|T28超重型坦克]]。<ref name="PACCAR: The Pursuit of Quality">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books/about/Paccar.html?id=IBCJAAAACAAJ|title=PACCAR: The Pursuit of Quality|last2=Provorse|first2=Barry|publisher=Documentary Media LLC|accessdate=2013-06-26|year=2005|isbn=978-0-971-90847-5|edition=4th|last1=Groner|first1=Alex|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220031033/https://books.google.com/books/about/Paccar.html?id=IBCJAAAACAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>Everett-Pacific造船和船坞公司成立于1942年，为[[埃弗雷特|埃弗雷特]]加德纳港湾的美国海军建造船只和其他海洋产品。它在1944年被Pacific Car收購。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://shipbuildinghistory.com/history/shipyards/4emergencysmall/everett.htm|title=Everett Pacific Shipbuilding|accessdate=2013-06-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127222828/http://www.shipbuildinghistory.com/history/shipyards/4emergencysmall/everett.htm|archivedate=2013-01-27}}</ref>

=== 战后 ===
[[File:Paccar's_History_in_the_early_1900.jpg|右]] (1950年)， 肯沃斯 T-10卡车和 [[T28超重型坦克|T28超重型坦克]] ([[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]])]]
第二次世界大战结束后,Pacific Car是联邦政府的动员计划的一部分,这意味着它承诺在全国进入紧急状态時投入100%的设施生产軍事器材。该公司在[[韓戰|韓戰]]期間是其中一个生产坦克的主要承包商。Pacific Car把合約中在細分和分包給很多中小企业。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.history.army.mil/documents/mobpam.htm|title=WWII Mobilization|accessdate=2013-06-20|publisher=U.S. Army Center of Military History|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316132102/http://history.army.mil/documents/mobpam.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://militaryvehicleweb.com/vehicle/m-26a1-pacific-car-tank-transporter-and-fruehauf-trailer/|title=1944 M-26A1 Pacific Car Tank Transporter and Fruehauf trailer|accessdate=2013-06-27|publisher=Militaryvehicleweb.com|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220031107/http://militaryvehicleweb.com/vehicle/m-26a1-pacific-car-tank-transporter-and-fruehauf-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1945年，Pacific Car收购Kenworth汽车公司。Kenworth自1923年成立以来一直在西雅图生产卡车。二战期间，Kenworth生产卡车、飞机配件和为美军提供配件。战争结束后Kenworth将注意力转移到战后商业卡车的生产市场。1956年Kenworth失去了独立地位，正式成为直属Pacific Car的一个部门。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitaltermpapers.com/c1074.htm|title=The History of Kenworth Motor Truck Company|accessdate=2013-06-15|publisher=Digital Term Papers|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304122754/http://www.digitaltermpapers.com/c1074.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1954年，Pacific Car收购了[[密苏里州|密苏里州]][[堪薩斯城_(密蘇里州)|堪萨斯城]]的Dart Truck Company和[[加州|加州]][[奥克兰_(加利福尼亚州)|奥克兰]]的{{tsl|en|Peterbilt}}汽车公司。Dart主要建造重型越野卡车和特种车辆；而Peterbilt就生产各种的卡车和公共汽车，並一直是Kenworth的主要竞争对手。<ref name="History of Paccar Inc">{{Cite web|url=http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/paccar-inc-history/|title=History of Paccar inc|accessdate=2013-06-27|publisher=Fundinguniverse.com|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220031111/http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/paccar-inc-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.peterbiltofla.com/history.html|title=Peterbilt History|accessdate=2013-06-27|publisher=Peterbilt of Louisiana|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731215438/http://www.peterbiltofla.com/history.html|archivedate=2013-07-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://prezi.com/gmr2uz5xeaso/the-history-of-peterbilt-trucks/|title=History of Peterbilt trucks|accessdate=2013-06-27|publisher=Peterbilt of Louisiana|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200647/https://prezi.com/gmr2uz5xeaso/the-history-of-peterbilt-trucks/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Pacific Car製造了用于构建Seattle-First National Bank总部和1961年的西雅图太空针塔的鋼材。该公司為[[纽约|纽约]]的[[世界贸易中心|世界贸易中心]]双子塔提供了5668塊钢面板，重达58000吨，構成主要的承重墙。這些钢面板經由铁路从西雅图到纽约市，動用超过1600個車卡。Pacific Car是为世界贸易中心提供了钢才的13間公司的最大承包商。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://digital.lib.washington.edu/architect/structures/4265/|title=Seattle 1st National Bank, Incorporated, Headquarters Building #2, Downtown|accessdate=2013-06-15|publisher=[[華盛頓州立大學|WSU Library]]|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714153417/https://digital.lib.washington.edu/architect/structures/4265/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://911research.wtc7.net/mirrors/guardian2/wtc/eng-news-record.htm|title=TRADE CENTER BUILDS UPWARD FAST|accessdate=2013-06-15|publisher=911research.wtc7.net|archive-date=2012-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120621212329/http://911research.wtc7.net/mirrors/guardian2/wtc/eng-news-record.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://guardian.150m.com/wtc/small/eng-news-record.htm|title=SOME ARTICLES FROM ENGINEERING NEWS RECORD.|accessdate=2013-06-15|publisher=guardian.150m.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121129115845/http://guardian.150m.com/wtc/small/eng-news-record.htm|archivedate=2012-11-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

=== 从1970年代到1990年代的挑战 ===
尽管1974年经济严重放缓，PACCAR的销售額在整个1970年代继续增加。PACCAR在1975年收購Wagner Mining Company，這家公司主要建造地下采矿车辆。1975年，收購了International Car Company。1980年，收購了英国卡车制造商{{tsl|en|Foden Trucks}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.atlascopco.com/us/news/productnews/atlas_copco__atlas_copco_wagner_inc.aspx|title=Wagner, The early years|accessdate=2013-06-25|publisher=[[阿特拉斯科普柯集团|Atlas Copco]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915230036/http://www.atlascopco.com/us/news/productnews/atlas_copco__atlas_copco_wagner_inc.aspx|archivedate=2016-09-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.lib.washington.edu/cgi-bin/showfile.exe?CISOROOT=/reports&CISOPTR=4452&CISOMODE=print|title=1982 PACCAR Annual Report|accessdate=2013-06-18|publisher=[[華盛頓州立大學|WSU Library]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216204255/http://content.lib.washington.edu/cgi-bin/showfile.exe?CISOROOT=%2Freports&CISOPTR=4452&CISOMODE=print|archivedate=2013-12-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hoovers.com/company/PACCAR_Inc/rcyhci-1-1njhxk.html|title=Paccar Inc, Company profile from Hoover's|accessdate=2013-06-28|publisher={{tsl|en|Hoover's||Hoover's}}}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.roadtransporthall.com/yesterdays-workhorses/1264-foden.html|title=Foden, yesterdays work horses|accessdate=2013-06-29|publisher=Road transport hall|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130410114612/http://www.roadtransporthall.com/yesterdays-workhorses/1264-foden.html|archivedate=2013-04-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gracesguide.co.uk/Foden|title=Edwin Foden, Sons and Co of Elworth Works, Sandbach produced commercial vehicles|accessdate=2013-06-29|publisher=Gracesguide.co.uk|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814114752/https://www.gracesguide.co.uk/Foden|dead-url=no}}</ref>PACCAR International于1972年成立，以出口其產品至全球各地。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.paccar.com/paccint/about-us.asp|title=History of Paccar International|accessdate=2013-06-28|publisher=Paccar International Inc|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200635/https://www.paccar.com/paccint/about-us.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/business/companies/paccar_inc/index.html|title=Paccar Inc News|accessdate=2013-06-28|publisher=[[纽约时报|NY Times]]|archive-date=2017-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701034019/http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/business/companies/paccar_inc/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>PACCAR技术中心于1980年在华盛顿州[[弗农山_(华盛顿州)|弗农山庄]]成立，作为研究和测试设施。技术中心每年4月舉行开放日。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tulipfestival.org/calendar/event/517/|title=PTC Open House|accessdate=2013-06-20|publisher=Tulipfestival.org|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130403065530/http://www.tulipfestival.org/calendar/event/517/|archivedate=2013-04-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.paccar.com/company/PTC_open_house.asp|title=PACCAR Tech Center Opn House|accessdate=2013-06-29|publisher=Paccar Inc|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130305115619/http://www.paccar.com/company/PTC_open_house.asp|archivedate=2013-03-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>1983年，International Car在[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[肯特_(俄亥俄州)|肯特]]的部門遭解散。<ref>1975 PACCAR Annual Report</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.upi.com/Archives/1983/02/18/The-International-Car-Co-once-a-leading-maker-of/1193414392400 |title=UPI February 18 1983 |access-date=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2019-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604080647/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1983/02/18/The-International-Car-Co-once-a-leading-maker-of/1193414392400/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1983年，PACCAR Rail Leasing在兰顿和[[贝尔维尤_(华盛顿州)|贝尔维尤]]的部門被解散。<ref>1982, 1983 PACCAR Annual Reports</ref>1986年，Pacific Car and Foundry改名为PACCAR防御系统部门。<ref>1985, 1986 PACCAR Annual Reports</ref>在1984年PACCAR实现了历史上创纪录的销售額 - 22.5亿美元。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1984/07/24/business/paccar-inc-reports-earnings-for-qtr-to-june-30.html|title=PACCAR INC reports earnings 