在1980年代中期，由于受{{tsl|en|Freightliner Trucks|Freightliner}}卡車的竞争，PACCAR {{tsl|en|Truck_classification#Class_8|Class 8}}卡车所占的份额下降到18%。这种竞争迫使PACCAR关闭Kenworth位於堪萨斯城的组装工厂和Peterbilt位於加州纽瓦克的工厂。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.lib.washington.edu/cgi-bin/showfile.exe?CISOROOT=/reports&CISOPTR=4119&CISOMODE=print|title=Pacific Car and Foundry Annual Report|accessdate=2013-06-30|publisher=[[華盛頓州立大學|WSU Library]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216203126/http://content.lib.washington.edu/cgi-bin/showfile.exe?CISOROOT=%2Freports&CISOPTR=4119&CISOMODE=print|archivedate=2013-12-16}}</ref>1986年，PACCAR以6500万美元收购位于加州嘉丁拿的石油勘探设备制造商Trico Industries。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1986/11/28/business/company-news-paccar-increases-its-stake-in-trico.html|title=COMPANY NEWS; PACCAR Increases Its Stake in Trico|date=1986-11-28|publisher=[[纽约时报|NY Times]]|accessdate=2013-06-26|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200809/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/11/28/business/company-news-paccar-increases-its-stake-in-trico.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/stories/1997/12/08/story5.html|title=Trico Industries sold to Evi Inc.|accessdate=2013-06-30|date=1997-12-07|publisher={{tsl|en|American City Business Journals||San Antonio Business Journal}}|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200727/https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/stories/1997/12/08/story5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在1980年代中期，PACCAR与[[Rover|Rover]]集团商討收購其英国的[[利蘭|利蘭]]卡车，但Rover最後决定改為把它出售予[[DAF|DAF卡车]]。1984年和1989年Dart Truck Company和Wagner Mining Equipment Company再次被出售。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sabcc.org/linked/blhistory.pdf|title=A brief history of British Leyland|accessdate=2013-06-30|publisher=Sabcc.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130228113641/http://www.sabcc.org/linked/blhistory.pdf|archivedate=2013-02-28|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.britishcarcouncil.com/history/bmc.html|title=British Leyland History|accessdate=2013-06-30|publisher=Britishcarcouncil.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403104518/http://www.britishcarcouncil.com/history/bmc.html|archivedate=2015-04-03}}</ref>1987年，PACCAR收购了Al’s Auto Supply和Grand Auto Incorporated，並进入汽车零件及配件零售市场。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1999/08/24/business/company-news-csk-auto-to-buy-paccar-s-parts-subsidiary.html|title=CSK Auto to buy Paccar parts subsidiary|date=1999-08-24|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2013-06-20|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200731/https://www.nytimes.com/1999/08/24/business/company-news-csk-auto-to-buy-paccar-s-parts-subsidiary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19990823&slug=2978949|title=PACCAR To Sell Auto-Parts Unit, Focus On Trucks|accessdate=2013-07-08|date=1999-08-23|publisher=The Seattle Times|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104212250/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19990823&slug=2978949|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/seattle/stories/1999/08/23/daily4.html|title=Paccar sells retail automotive parts group|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=1999-08-23|publisher={{tsl|en|Puget Sound Business Journal||Puget Sound Business Journal}}|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807200803/https://www.bizjournals.com/seattle/stories/1999/08/23/daily4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

